(63, 1, '2020-12-10 10:30:44', '2020-12-10 10:30:44', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The Human Codex - the future of human history.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Human Codex aims to be the first ever human history record of the people, created by the people, for the people. Its purpose is simple, it is a place where everyone can come and leave their own personal mark in history. Visitors of the site/app will be given the ability to create their own digital time capsule (called a Codex) which will allow them to record any significant life events such as Birthdays; Weddings etc. Photos and videos can be saved to your Codex.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are asking people to document their lives in a way they want to be remembered. Our hope is that future generations will get to see the true likeness of the people of our time and also to learn from our life experiences. For the first time, the people of this planet can choose the way they want to be remembered and The Human Codex will be giving them that opportunity, for free!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":169,\"width\":960,\"height\":540,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-rounded\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/title.jpg\" alt=\"The Human Codex - Guiding our future by sharing your past\" class=\"wp-image-169\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Find out more and see if The Human Codes is a project you want to participate in. Explore the site and get in touch if you would like to be a Beta tester or help with the project itself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Human Codex', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'thehumancodex-home', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:05:44', '2020-12-14 12:05:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/?page_id=63', 0, 'page', '', 0),
