(118, 1, '2020-12-11 10:26:20', '2020-12-11 10:26:20', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">The Human Codex - the future of human history</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Human Codex aims to be the first ever human history record of the people, created by the people, for the people. Its purpose is simple, it is a place where everyone can come and leave their own personal mark in history. Visitors of the site/app will be given the ability to create their own digital time capsule (called a Codex) which will allow them to record any significant life events such as Birthdays; Weddings etc. Photos and videos can be saved to the Codex.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are asking people to document their lives in a way they want to be remembered. Our hope is that future generations will get to see the true likeness of the people of our time and also to learn from our life experiences. For the first time, the people of this planet can choose the way they want to be remembered and The Human Codex will be giving them that opportunity, for free!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":71,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2018-10-04-26-1.png\" alt=\"The Human Codex\" class=\"wp-image-71\"/><figcaption>A global unifying project</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Find out more and see if The Human Codes is a project you want to participate in. Explore the site and get in touch if you would like to be a Beta tester or help with the project itself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Human Codex', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '63-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-11 10:26:20', '2020-12-11 10:26:20', '', 63, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/63-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(121, 1, '2020-12-11 10:31:35', '2020-12-11 10:31:35', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The Human Codex - the future of human history.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Human Codex aims to be the first ever human history record of the people, created by the people, for the people. Its purpose is simple, it is a place where everyone can come and leave their own personal mark in history. Visitors of the site/app will be given the ability to create their own digital time capsule (called a Codex) which will allow them to record any significant life events such as Birthdays; Weddings etc. Photos and videos can be saved to the Codex.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are asking people to document their lives in a way they want to be remembered. Our hope is that future generations will get to see the true likeness of the people of our time and also to learn from our life experiences. For the first time, the people of this planet can choose the way they want to be remembered and The Human Codex will be giving them that opportunity, for free!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":71,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2018-10-04-26-1.png\" alt=\"The Human Codex\" class=\"wp-image-71\"/><figcaption>A global unifying project</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Find out more and see if The Human Codes is a project you want to participate in. Explore the site and get in touch if you would like to be a Beta tester or help with the project itself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Human Codex', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '63-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-11 10:31:35', '2020-12-11 10:31:35', '', 63, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/63-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(122, 1, '2020-12-11 10:37:45', '2020-12-11 10:37:45', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>THE HUMAN CODEX EXPLAINED</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Human Codex,  essentially a digital time capsule, which we created to make use of the known and often respected cultural practice of having ordinary individuals or traditional, often small communities, lock away details relevant to their importance so that they can be opened later. This practice is considered almost sacred in many ways because it has been shown to be an effective way to connect the present or future to the past and help ensure that history doesnt forget those who made society strong.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Historically, time capsules have been important tools that carried a kind of reverence for the past and towards the future. People were excited and anxious about what is inside the locked and buried devices, hoping that once opened they will clarify uncertainties and give them a better sense of the past. Today, technology plays a similar role, or it did before we became so flooded with digital inundation that we have lost touch with the spiritual and uplifting elements of what gets stored.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ct2Q4aJpdCM\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ct2Q4aJpdCM\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>THC seeks to return this quality to our users and will, in so doing, increase the value of the information contained inside each users capsule. Large-scale genealogy and family history platforms are built using uniform programming that tries the details together in ways that conform to business and large data needs. Similarly, online encyclopaedic resources such as Wikipedia build collections of facts and details to make a library-like collection of information. But what of us as people, as people who live our own stories and recall our own truths about our adventures?&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Human Codex will share many elements of other journaling and personal or family heritage portals. But we also believe that our model will be different, most importantly as it will allow users to decide for themselves what information to keep and how to put it together into their story as they lived and experienced it. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In many ways, we are coming to respect technologies data-gathering capabilities at the same time that we worry about how government, corporate, and cyber enterprises are seeking to collect details about us to construct and image of us that serves their interests.&nbsp;Googling the phrase time capsule (July 2018) provides a historical and cultural explanation of this practice and is worth reviewing. But it also offers an empowering qualification that plays well with THC, as this quote validates: <em>Historians suggest that items which describe the daily lives of the people who created them, such as personal notes, pictures, and documents, would greatly increase the value of the time capsule to future historians</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>ORIGINS</strong> </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>THC began as a frustration in 2015. Why cant our individual stories be as prominent and as important as stories made up by business and information interests? After up and down trials, it became evident that there was a lot of passion and commitment that wanted to get behind such an ideal.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Human Codex (Company number: 10642472) was incorporated in February 2017 under the directives of The Companies Act 2006 as a Community Interest Company Limited by Guarantee. This enabled us to begin developing as a not-for-profit enterprise.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>TECHNOLOGY</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><br></strong>In order to ensure that our platform is user-easy and adaptable to a wide-range of input and evolution, we have opted to develop the site using the most popular and modern backend framework PHP called Laravel, making THC a MVC Web application. Our application works with Google API\'s to provide Geocoding and Place Autocomplete. We are storing data in a MySQL database via Eloquent ORM. Frontend of this application is based on Vue.js. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The special programming creates a digital time capsule that preserves memories in sharable formats. The data will be maintained to facilitate a true likeness of how the users lived their lives and will document information chronologically and geographically. The news feed will be usable either on the typical wall, or through a map. It will show contacts and connections about where they are and where they are going in their adventure. There will not be suggested posts, thus encouraging people to create their own. There will be a self-analysis page to raise awareness and help keep the story moving forward.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":57,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/globe-1024x477.jpg\" alt=\"The Human Codex\" class=\"wp-image-57\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About the Human Codex', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-11 10:37:45', '2020-12-11 10:37:45', '', 34, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(128, 1, '2020-12-11 10:41:59', '2020-12-11 10:41:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please find our contact form below. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":71,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2018-10-04-26-1.png\" alt=\"contact\" class=\"wp-image-71\"/><figcaption>People from around the world</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:tw/form-maker {\"shortcode\":\"[Form id=\\u00221\\u0022]\",\"popupOpened\":false,\"notInitial\":true} -->\n[Form id=\"1\"]\n<!-- /wp:tw/form-maker -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '97-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-11 10:41:59', '2020-12-11 10:41:59', '', 97, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/97-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
