(201, 1, '2020-12-14 09:08:27', '2020-12-14 09:08:27', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As part of our early operationalizing, we put together a governing board and began to develop and refine specific goals and objectives. The specifics of these visions are evolving as the scope of our dream has grown. We have identified the following general guiding expectations for our beginning year of implementation:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Create a self-sustaining platform where users can record their life stories.</li><li>Reach out to connect people from different walks of life such that they understand and can begin using the site.</li><li>Retain an emphasis on creating a unique addition to the history record that is truthful and honest to individual visions of their lives and that is less tainted by external interests that can extend to using personal stories for greed, corruption, or self-interests.</li><li>Offer to a broad reach of society a form of digital immortality.</li><li>Help create a better future by asking the people to share their pasts, so that those who come after us can learn early what we learn later in life.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our early efforts are directed at getting the platform fully usable. As this happens, we will be able to follow unique ancillary opportunities as well. For example, filling in the details of ones like in a step-by-step way (like chapters in a book) gives meaning that can be important between generations, for making sense of family incidents and activities, for documenting behaviours that might help persons with medical conditions, etc. We also believe that THC will become a critical resource for online citizen and conventional journalists who discover stories that need a human element. Taken together, these truths become important in adding order to our many experiences.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:envira/envira-gallery {\"galleryId\":158,\"title\":\"App designs\",\"columns\":\"0\",\"row_height\":150,\"lightbox_enabled\":1,\"lazyload_enabled\":1,\"lightbox_theme\":\"base\",\"images\":[{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/globe-scaled.jpg\",\"title\":\"Profile globe\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/globe-scaled.jpg\",\"alt\":\"globe profile\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":137,\"height\":130.12259194395796,\"width\":279.8},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2017-09-16-6-300x169.png\",\"title\":\"2017-09-16 (6)\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2017-09-16-6.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":161,\"height\":130.12259194395796,\"width\":231.6},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/profile-map-hd-3-300x169.png\",\"title\":\"profile-map-hd (3)\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/profile-map-hd-3.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":162,\"height\":130.12259194395796,\"width\":231.6},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/News-feed.jpg\",\"title\":\"News feed\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/News-feed.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":163,\"height\":170.09132420091325,\"width\":372.5},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Timeline-1.jpg\",\"title\":\"Timeline\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Timeline-1.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":164,\"height\":170.09132420091325,\"width\":372.5},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Activity-view.jpg\",\"title\":\"Activity view\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Activity-view.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":165,\"height\":137.847866419295,\"width\":301.9},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.02.-Profile-Connections-More-300x212.jpg\",\"title\":\"07.02. Profile \\u0026#8211; Connections \\u0026#8211; More\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.02.-Profile-Connections-More.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":166,\"height\":137.847866419295,\"width\":195.7},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.07.-Profile-Globe-300x169.jpg\",\"title\":\"07.07. Profile \\u0026#8211; Globe\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.07.-Profile-Globe.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":167,\"height\":137.847866419295,\"width\":245.4}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-envira-envira-gallery\">[envira-gallery id=\'158\']</div>\n<!-- /wp:envira/envira-gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Vision</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The world is ever changing and technology is becoming more and more interlinked with our lives. Unfortunately, a lot of big tech companies exploit their users, mainly without their users ever really knowing. We are creating our platform so that even if we have the same intentions ( we do not) this is not possible. With our integrated user reporting system, where the users are in control and decide what posts/ Codex break the community rules and which users are spamming, or participating in illegal actions, we will then act accordingly. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are a not for profit organisation and once we become a self-sustaining platform we want to use any excess revenue to help humanity reach the SDG 2020 goals. Each user will be allocated the same percentage of excess revenue and will be able to vote to where they would like it to be donated to. We want to use as much of our resources as we can to help create a better world for each of us, and those who come after us.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Goals</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the later stages of the project and if we are able to reach our goals, the users will be in control of how the platform is run, which features are introduced, which direction the organisation heads and/ if anything, how much those who work for the organisation will be remunerated. We are not trying to become the next \"tech unicorn\" we are trying to create a platform, a service an entity that can not be corrupted from the inside, or the out that will last as long as humanity exists. <br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We believe our core function, or recording human history of the people. by the people for the people, will allow us to achieve what we have listed above. We may not live to see the results of what we are setting out to do, but we fully understand the importance of planting trees that we will not eat the fruit from. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":136,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2018-10-04-26.png\" alt=\"Goals unifying the human race\" class=\"wp-image-136\"/><figcaption>People of the world coming together </figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Vision and goals', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-14 09:08:27', '2020-12-14 09:08:27', '', 54, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/54-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
