(237, 1, '2020-12-14 12:03:29', '2020-12-14 12:03:29', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When we first started I was so excited, I had finally found someone to make The Human Codex the way I wanted, who understood the concept, except what I kept thinking it was all too good to be true. Which later turned out to be the case. Long Story cut short, I found myself over a year down the line with nothing to show and funds gone. So, in February 2017, the developer and The Human Codex went their separate ways.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the meantime, I met Domagoj (October 2016). We had both signed up to participate in a project to do with Space, which I subsequently felt like I had to leave in order to protect &amp; concentrate on The Human Codex. When Domagoj and I first started speaking, it was as if we had known each other for a long time. We instantly became friends and I think we have spoken pretty much every day since. Domagoj kindly offered to take a look at what I had for The Human Codex so far and taught me some basics about web development. Liking the concept and my vision for the application, He later agreed to be our new developer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Within a week of Domagoj as the new THC Developer, we had a single page up for the public, so they could finally see what we were trying to accomplish (this is down now while we update to WordPress). We spoke about THC nonstop and together worked out a solid foundation. Also, as our friendship continued to grow, we were able to help one another with personal issues that arose along the way (we all have them!).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Alongside all of this, I had been experiencing some problems with my day job. The problems appeared to be manageable at first but seemed to deteriorate further after August 2016 when I received some life-changing news. After what felt like a very rough time in my life in June 2017 I decided to focus solely on The Human Codex.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It wasnt completely solely my choice but I knew the time had come to make a decision, it was time to take what turned out to be one of if not the most crucial step so far.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nothing had prepared me for what was to come next, I had to face one of my biggest fears, my own mind.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":236,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/In-the-Beginning-1024x640.jpeg\" alt=\"In the Beginning\" class=\"wp-image-236\"/><figcaption>In the Beginning</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'In the Beginning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '76-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:03:29', '2020-12-14 12:03:29', '', 76, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/76-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(239, 1, '2020-12-14 12:04:36', '2020-12-14 12:04:36', '', 'despair', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'despair', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:04:36', '2020-12-14 12:04:36', '', 87, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/despair.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(240, 1, '2020-12-14 12:05:09', '2020-12-14 12:05:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So much has happened since our last blog - It is about time we posted an update for you all!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Firstly, I want to say thank you to everyone who continues to follow and support The Human Codex. Your patience while waiting for the Core to be released is greatly appreciated  we want it to be as good as it can be for you and will be sure to let you know as soon as its ready for users.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since our last posts, we sold our house and moved to Croatia to be closer to the development team. It was hard leaving our friends and family, particularly just before Christmas, but it was to be our biggest adventure yet and we were excited to be moving full steam ahead with The Human Codex. The flight was a bit of an ordeal, for both us and the cats, but eventually we all got there!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We rented a house in Osijek from a very nice guy. There wasnt anything that he wouldnt do to help out and despite neither of us being able to speak each others language, we made it work. We dedicated one of the rooms in the house to be the THC workspace and kitted it out with desks, chairs, equipment etc. Everything felt as though it could be finally be falling into place but we should have known that something so worthwhile wouldnt be that easy</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In April 2018, our Designer (Marko Boskavic) and our Front-end developer (Domagoj Buljan) departed the team. I would love to say that this was on good terms, but it wasnt. Both took money from The Humam Codex and then didnt bother to complete their tasks to finish the core, which they were contracted to do. Domagoj, in particular, is a psychopath and a scam artist. That may sound unprofessional and perhaps a bit harsh to some people, but when you receive numerous threats and the only way you can sleep for weeks is to have a knife by your side just in case it takes a lot to put it as nicely as I have.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Losing our front-end developer wasnt the best situation to be in however, luckily for us, we had also been liaising with another developer who had expressed an interest in working with us. He seemed keen, had many ideas and was looking for work  the timing was perfect!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Despite this, we took the decision to flee Osijek and head towards Split on the coast of Croatia. Both the back-end and newly appointment Front-end developer agreed to continue their work with us remotely, so it was just a case of maintaining communication with them in order to avoid delays and keep things moving forward. It seemed as though, despite a few delays, we were back on track.<br><br>Unfortunately, that feeling didnt last long. Once we had left Osijek, we contacted our newly appointed Front-end Developer on numerous occasions trying to get updates etc to which we either received no response or excuses days later. Time was of the essence and we couldnt afford to keep waiting on him. This departure was actually extremely disappointing for us as we had genuinely thought he had been committed to THC. In addition, we knew that it would take time to find a replacement so either way work on THC was going to experience another delay.<br><br>Despite being in such a beautiful setting, this was probably our lowest moment working on THC. Everything felt like a struggle and we were tired of the constant battle. Our faith in humanity had been diminishing with each day and the reasons for carrying on were no longer clear. It was a dark time to say the least.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During this time, we also had to think about what the future held for us personally. We had invested a lot of our money into bringing THC to life and had to start considering the best way to use the remaining funds to live We came up with the idea of touring, so that we could slowly make our way back to the UK without having to put the cats through the trauma of another flight and also get to see a little of Europe on the way  perfect! So I headed back to the UK for a weekend in the middle of May, picked up a car and a caravan with my dad and returned to Croatia with them. I had never driven in Europe or towed a Caravan before, so the prospect was scary but still, an adventure.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Founder and I had agreed that, while I was away, we would both think long and hard about whether or not to continue with The Human Codex. There had been so many obstacles and it became very tiring, always fighting to move forward.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>BUT, if nothing else, we are determined! We feel that people could really benefit from using THC and it is our duty to get it out there. So upon my return, we started the hunt for a new Front-end Developer. The Founder had actually been in conversation with a friend who said that he could recommend someone. After so many knock backs, we tried not to get our hopes up, but this seemed to be the lifeline we were waiting for.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The new developer caught quickly up to speed with where the platform was at and began work to help finish what we started all those years ago!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Luckily, throughout all this, we also had a brilliant back-end developer and he kindly introduced us to a designer that he knew, who has turned out to be very professional and equally brilliant! Based on his knowledge and experience he has created a new design for The Human Codex and this is what we are currently working on implementing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, after the craziest 8 months, we are now back in the UK working remotely with the team. The journey has been anything but easybut we are still here, now stronger and wiser than before.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":239,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/despair-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"We had no way of knowing\" class=\"wp-image-239\"/><figcaption>We had no way of knowing</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'We had no way of knowing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:05:09', '2020-12-14 12:05:09', '', 87, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/87-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(242, 1, '2020-12-14 12:05:43', '2020-12-14 12:05:43', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The Human Codex - the future of human history.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Human Codex aims to be the first ever human history record of the people, created by the people, for the people. Its purpose is simple, it is a place where everyone can come and leave their own personal mark in history. Visitors of the site/app will be given the ability to create their own digital time capsule (called a Codex) which will allow them to record any significant life events such as Birthdays; Weddings etc. Photos and videos can be saved to your Codex.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iV46zT0468\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are asking people to document their lives in a way they want to be remembered. Our hope is that future generations will get to see the true likeness of the people of our time and also to learn from our life experiences. For the first time, the people of this planet can choose the way they want to be remembered and The Human Codex will be giving them that opportunity, for free!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":169,\"width\":960,\"height\":540,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-rounded\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/title.jpg\" alt=\"The Human Codex - Guiding our future by sharing your past\" class=\"wp-image-169\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Find out more and see if The Human Codes is a project you want to participate in. Explore the site and get in touch if you would like to be a Beta tester or help with the project itself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Human Codex', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '63-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:05:43', '2020-12-14 12:05:43', '', 63, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/63-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(244, 1, '2020-12-14 12:06:28', '2020-12-14 12:06:28', '<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":199,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/privacy.jpg\" alt=\"Privacy Policy\" class=\"wp-image-199\"/><figcaption>Privacy Policy</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>THE HUMAN CODEX LIMITED</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Background and information about this privacy policy</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1.1 This privacy policy sets out our commitment to maintaining the privacy and security of our website visitors and the users of our services.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1.2 We have prepared this policy to clearly set out and explain how we will safeguard and process your personal data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1.3 As soon as you visit our website, we will ask you to give your consent to allow is to use cookies. We have a cookie policy on our website and all cookies will be used by us strictly in accordance with that policy which may be updated from time to time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1.4 You control your privacy, and this will affect the way in which we process any personal data you give to us. You can specify what we can do with your personal data, such as using it for marketing and other purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1.5 Information about us and how to contact us is set out at the end of this policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>How we will use your personal data</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.1 In this paragraph we have set out information about:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.1.1 the categories of personal data that we may process in the course of our business;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.1.2 the purposes for which we may process your personal data; and</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.1.3 the legal grounds for our processing of your personal data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.2 We may, as part of our business activities, process data about you as well as your use of our and access to our website and services (\"Your Data\"). Included within Your Data will be your IP address, geographical location, the type and version of any browser you use to visit our website, your devices operating system, referral source, the length of your visit to our website, details of the pages of our website that you view and website the paths you follow when navigating our website, as well as information about the timing, frequency and pattern of your visits to our website and the use of our services. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As such, Your Data may be processed by us for the purposes of analysing your use of, or access to, our website and services. The legal basis for this processing is our legitimate interests, namely the provision of our services and availability of our website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>3.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Data used for the provision of our services&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.1 We may process Your Data as provided by you in the course of the use of our services (<strong>\"</strong>Your Service Data\"). Your Service Data will be provided to us by you. Your Service Data may be processed by us for the purposes of:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.1.1 operating our website;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.1.2 providing our services;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.1.3 ensuring the security of our website and services;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.1.4 maintaining back-ups of our databases; and&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.1.5 communicating with you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;3.2 The legal basis for this processing is our legitimate interests, namely the provision of our services and availability of our website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>4.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Data used for opening an account with us</strong><strong></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4.1 If you choose to open an account with us, then we may process your account data (\"Your Account Data\") as part of the provision of our services to you. Your Account Data may include personal data such as your name and email address. You agree that you are the source and provider of Your Account Data which is being provided to us for scientific or historical research purposes or statistical purposes on grounds relating to your particular situation, unless the processing is necessary for the performance of a task carried out for reasons of public interest to us. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your Account Data may be processed by us to enable us to operate our website, provide our services to you, ensure and maintain the security of our website and services and maintain back-ups of our databases and all communications with you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4.2 The legal basis for this processing is consent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>5.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Personal profile</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5.1 You may be required to create a personal profile on our website to use some of our services. We may process the information which you include in your personal profile on our website (\"Your Profile Data\") to enable us to provide our services to you. Your Profile Data may include information such as your name, address, telephone number, email address, profile pictures, images, gender, date of birth, relationship status, interests and hobbies, educational details and employment details.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5.2 Your Profile Data may be processed for by us the purposes of enabling and monitoring your use of our website and our services.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5.3 The legal basis for this processing is consent</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>6.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Data about transactions between you and us</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>6.1 We may process information, including your personal data, relating to transactions, including purchases by you of goods and services, that you enter into with us via our website (\"Transaction Data\"). Transaction Data may include personal data such as your contact details, your credit or debit card details and details and information about any relevant transaction. Transaction Data may be processed for the purpose of supplying to you the purchased goods and services, and for keeping proper records of those transactions.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>6.2 The legal basis for this processing is the performance of a contract between you and us and/or taking steps, at your request, to enter into such a contract.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>7.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Enquiries made by you on our website</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>7.1 We may process your personal data if it is contained in any enquiry you submit to us regarding products and/or services (\"Enquiry Data\"). Any Enquiry Data may be processed by us for the purposes of offering, marketing and selling relevant products and/or services to you.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>7.2 The legal basis for this processing is consent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>8.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Data published by you on our website</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>8.1 We may process information that you post for publication on our website or through our services (\"Your Publication Data\"). Your Publication Data may be processed for the purposes of enabling such publication and administering our website and services.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>8.2 The legal basis for this processing is consent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>9.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Notifications and newsletters</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>9.1 We may process personal data that you provide to us for the purpose of subscribing to our email notifications and/or newsletters (\"Your Notification Data\"). You agree that we may process Your Notification Data for the purposes of sending you the relevant notifications and/or newsletters.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>9.2 The legal basis for this processing is our legitimate interests, namely notification to you of information about our services which may be of interest to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>10.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Personal data and general communication between us</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>10.1 We may process personal data which is contained in or relating to any communication that you send to us (\"Correspondence Data\"). The Correspondence Data may include the communication content and metadata associated with the communication. Our website will generate the metadata associated with communications made with us by you using the contact forms which can be found on our website. Correspondence Data may be processed by us for the purposes of communicating with you and for the purposes of our own internal record-keeping.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>10.2 The legal basis for this processing is The legal basis for this processing is our legitimate interests, namely communication between you and us.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>11.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Required processing of personal data&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>11.1 We may process any of your personal data identified in the other provisions of this policy where necessary for the establishment, exercise or defence of legal claims, whether in court proceedings or in an administrative or out-of-court procedure.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>11.2 The legal basis for this processing is our legitimate interests, namely the protection and assertion of our legal rights, your legal rights and the legal rights of others.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>12.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Providing your personal data to others</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>12.1 We may, from time to time, need to disclose your personal data to our insurers and/or any of our professional advisers. This would only happen insofar as reasonably necessary for the purposes of us obtaining and maintaining insurance coverage, managing risks, obtaining professional advice and managing legal disputes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>12.2 There may be circumstances where we may need to disclose your personal data to some of our suppliers or subcontractors. If we do this, then it will only be insofar as reasonably necessary.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>12.3 We may disclose any personal data you provide to us in respect of any enquiry by you about our website or our services to one or more of our selected third-party suppliers of any services we provide as set out on our website. This would be strictly for the purpose of enabling such suppliers to contact you so that they can offer, market and sell to relevant goods and/or services to you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In these circumstances, each such third party will act as a data controller in relation to the personal data provided by you in respect of your enquiry that we supply to them and upon contacting you, each such third party will provide you with a copy of their own privacy policy. The third partys privacy policy will then govern that third party\'s use of your personal data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>12.4 As well as for the specific disclosures of personal data set out above in this clause 12, we may also disclose your personal data where such disclosure is necessary or required for us to comply with a legal obligation to which we are subject, or for us to protect your interests or the interests of another natural person.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>13.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Transfers of your personal data outside of the EEA</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>13.1 This clause sets out information about the circumstances in which we may transfer your personal data to countries outside of the European Economic Area (EEA).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>13.2 Our offices are in the United Kingdom. Transfers of personal data to countries outside of the EEA will be protected by appropriate safeguards, such as the use of standard data protection clauses adopted or approved by the European Commission.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>13.3 The hosting facilities for our website are situated in <em>[specify countries]</em>. Transfers to [<em>specify country</em>] will be protected by appropriate safeguards, such as the use of standard data protection clauses adopted or approved by the European Commission.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>13.4 You agree and acknowledge that when you submit any personal data via our website or services for general publication, then such information may be available, via the internet, anywhere in the world. In this case, you agree and acknowledge that we cannot prevent the use (or misuse) of such personal data by others.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>14.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>What we do about retaining and deleting your personal data</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>14.1 Our retention and deletion procedures are designed to help ensure that we comply with our legal obligations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>14.2 Any personal data which we process will not be kept for longer than is absolutely necessary for the purpose or purposes in respect of which we are processing such data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>14.3 We will retain your personal data for a reasonable period and for no longer than is necessary for us to process it, after which time we shall delete it from our systems.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>14.4 Notwithstanding the other provisions of this clause, we may retain your personal data where such retention is necessary for compliance with a legal obligation to which we are subject, or in order to protect your interests or the interests of another natural person.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>15.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Amendments to this privacy policy</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>15.1 We may update this privacy policy from time to time by publishing a new and updated version from time to time on our website. Please check back from time to time to ensure you are happy with any changes to this privacy policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>15.2 We may choose to notify you of changes to this policy by email or through the private messaging system on our website, but this may not always be the case.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>16.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Your rights in regard to your personal data</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.1 In this clause 16, we have set out the rights that you have as an individual under data protection law. Some of the rights are complicated and can be tricky to understand, and not all of the details have been included in our summaries. As such, we recommend that you read the relevant laws and guidance from the regulatory authorities for a full explanation of these rights.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2 Your principal rights under data protection law are:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.1 the right to access;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.2 the right to rectification;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.3 the right to erasure;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.4 the right to restrict processing;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.5 the right to object to processing;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.6 the right to data portability;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.7 the right to complain to a supervisory authority; and</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.2.8 the right to withdraw consent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.3 You have the right to request from us confirmation in respect of whether or not we process your personal data and, in circumstances where we do, access to the personal data, together with certain additional information. That additional information includes details of the purposes of our processing of your personal data, the categories of personal data concerned and the recipients of the personal data. Provided that in doing so the rights and freedoms of others are not affected, we will supply you with a copy of your personal data when requested by you to do so. The first copy will be provided to you free of charge, but additional copies may be subject to us charging a reasonable fee.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.4 You have the right to have any inaccurate personal data which we store about you rectified and, taking into account the purposes of our processing of that personal data, to have any incomplete personal data stored by us about you completed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.5 In certain circumstances you have the right to the request the erasure of your personal data without undue delay. Those circumstances include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.5.1 the personal data we are storing is no longer necessary in relation to the purposes for which they were collected or otherwise processed by us;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.5.2 you withdraw consent to processing which is consent based;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.5.3 the processing is for direct marketing purposes;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.5.4 and the personal data has been unlawfully processed.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.6 There are certain general exclusions of the right to erasure. Those general exclusions include where processing is necessary for the following reasons:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.6.1 exercising the right of freedom of expression and information;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.6.2 compliance with a legal obligation; or&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.6.3 for the establishment, exercise or defence of legal claims.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.7 In some circumstances you have the right to restrict the processing of your personal data. Those circumstances are as follows:&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.7.1 you contest the accuracy of the personal data being processed;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.7.2 the processing is unlawful, but you oppose its erasure;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.7.3 we no longer need the personal data for the purposes of our processing, but you require personal data for the establishment, exercise or defence of legal claims; and&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.7.4 you have objected to the processing of your personal data, pending the verification of that objection.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.8 Where processing of your personal data by us has been restricted on the basis set out in clause 16.7 above, we may continue to store your personal data. In this situation, we will only otherwise process your personal data:&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.8.1 with your consent;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.8.2 for the establishment, exercise or defence of legal claims;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.8.3 for the protection of the rights of another natural or legal person; or&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.8.4 for reasons of important public interest.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.9 You have the right to object to the processing of your personal data by us on grounds relating to your particular situation. However, you may only object to the extent that the legal basis for the processing is that the processing is necessary for:&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.9.1 the performance of a task carried out in the public interest or in the exercise of any official authority vested in us; or&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.9.2 the purposes of the legitimate interests pursued by us or by a third party.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.10 If you make an objection as set out in clause 16.9 above, we will cease to process your personal data unless we can demonstrate that there are compelling legitimate grounds for the processing which overrides your interests, rights and freedoms, or the processing is for the establishment, exercise or defence of legal claims.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.11 You have the right to object to our processing of your personal data:&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.11.1 for direct marketing purposes (including where we undertake profiling for the purposes of direct marketing). If you make such an objection, we will cease to process your personal data for this purpose;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.11.2 for scientific or historical research purposes or statistical purposes on grounds relating to your particular situation, unless the processing is necessary for the performance of a task carried out for reasons of public interest.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.12 To the extent that the legal basis for our processing of your personal data is consent, and such processing is carried out by automated means, you have the right to receive your personal data from us in a structured, commonly used and machine-readable format. However, this right does not apply where it would adversely affect the rights and freedoms of others.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.13 If you consider that our processing of your personal information infringes any data protection laws, then you have a legal right to make a complaint about that processing with a supervisory authority responsible for data protection. You may do so in the EU member state of your habitual residence, your place of work or the place of the alleged infringement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.14 To the extent that consent is the legal basis for our processing of your personal data, you have the right to withdraw that consent at any time. Withdrawal of consent by you will not affect the lawfulness of any processing by us before the withdrawal.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>16.15 You may exercise any of your rights in relation to your personal data by written notice to us in addition to the other methods specified in this clause 7.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>17.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>All about us and how to get in touch</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>17.1 This website is owned and operated by The Human Codex Limited<em>.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>17.2 We are registered in England and Wales under registration number 10642472 , and our registered office is at 6 Viewpoint Office Village, Babbage Road, Stevenage, Hertfordshire SG1 2EQ, United Kingdom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>17.3 Our principal place of business is at 6 Viewpoint Office Village, Babbage Road, Stevenage, Hertfordshire SG1 2EQ, United Kingdom.<em>&nbsp;</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>17.4 You can contact us:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>17.4.1 by post, using the postal address given above;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>17.4.2 using our website contact form;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>17.4.3 by email, using the email address published on our website from time to time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:06:28', '2020-12-14 12:06:28', '', 3, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/3-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
