(245, 1, '2020-12-14 12:06:49', '2020-12-14 12:06:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As part of our early operationalizing, we put together a governing board and began to develop and refine specific goals and objectives. The specifics of these visions are evolving as the scope of our dream has grown. We have identified the following general guiding expectations for our beginning year of implementation:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Create a self-sustaining platform where users can record their life stories.</li><li>Reach out to connect people from different walks of life such that they understand and can begin using the site.</li><li>Retain an emphasis on creating a unique addition to the history record that is truthful and honest to individual visions of their lives and that is less tainted by external interests that can extend to using personal stories for greed, corruption, or self-interests.</li><li>Offer to a broad reach of society a form of digital immortality.</li><li>Help create a better future by asking the people to share their pasts, so that those who come after us can learn early what we learn later in life.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":204,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/vision.jpg\" alt=\"Vision\" class=\"wp-image-204\"/><figcaption>Number of 2020 to 2022 on asphalt road surface with marking lines</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our early efforts are directed at getting the platform fully usable. As this happens, we will be able to follow unique ancillary opportunities as well. For example, filling in the details of ones like in a step-by-step way (like chapters in a book) gives meaning that can be important between generations, for making sense of family incidents and activities, for documenting behaviours that might help persons with medical conditions, etc. We also believe that THC will become a critical resource for online citizen and conventional journalists who discover stories that need a human element. Taken together, these truths become important in adding order to our many experiences.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:envira/envira-gallery {\"galleryId\":158,\"title\":\"App designs\",\"columns\":\"0\",\"row_height\":150,\"lightbox_enabled\":1,\"lazyload_enabled\":1,\"lightbox_theme\":\"base\",\"images\":[{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/globe-scaled.jpg\",\"title\":\"Profile globe\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/globe-scaled.jpg\",\"alt\":\"globe profile\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":137,\"height\":143.1645569620253,\"width\":307.8},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2017-09-16-6-300x169.png\",\"title\":\"2017-09-16 (6)\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2017-09-16-6.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":161,\"height\":143.1645569620253,\"width\":254.8},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/profile-map-hd-3-300x169.png\",\"title\":\"profile-map-hd (3)\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/profile-map-hd-3.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":162,\"height\":143.1645569620253,\"width\":254.8},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/News-feed.jpg\",\"title\":\"News feed\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/News-feed.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":163,\"height\":143.1645569620253,\"width\":313.5},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Timeline-1.jpg\",\"title\":\"Timeline\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Timeline-1.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":164,\"height\":149.2084432717678,\"width\":326.8},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Activity-view.jpg\",\"title\":\"Activity view\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Activity-view.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":165,\"height\":149.2084432717678,\"width\":326.8},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.02.-Profile-Connections-More-300x212.jpg\",\"title\":\"07.02. Profile \\u0026#8211; Connections \\u0026#8211; More\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.02.-Profile-Connections-More.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":166,\"height\":149.2084432717678,\"width\":211.9},{\"status\":\"active\",\"src\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.07.-Profile-Globe-300x169.jpg\",\"title\":\"07.07. Profile \\u0026#8211; Globe\",\"link\":\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/07.07.-Profile-Globe.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"id\":167,\"height\":149.2084432717678,\"width\":265.6}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-envira-envira-gallery\">[envira-gallery id=\'158\']</div>\n<!-- /wp:envira/envira-gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Vision</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The world is ever changing and technology is becoming more and more interlinked with our lives. Unfortunately, a lot of big tech companies exploit their users, mainly without their users ever really knowing. We are creating our platform so that even if we have the same intentions ( we do not) this is not possible. With our integrated user reporting system, where the users are in control and decide what posts/ Codex break the community rules and which users are spamming, or participating in illegal actions, we will then act accordingly. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are a not for profit organisation and once we become a self-sustaining platform we want to use any excess revenue to help humanity reach the SDG 2020 goals. Each user will be allocated the same percentage of excess revenue and will be able to vote to where they would like it to be donated to. We want to use as much of our resources as we can to help create a better world for each of us, and those who come after us.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Goals</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the later stages of the project and if we are able to reach our goals, the users will be in control of how the platform is run, which features are introduced, which direction the organisation heads and/ if anything, how much those who work for the organisation will be remunerated. We are not trying to become the next \"tech unicorn\" we are trying to create a platform, a service an entity that can not be corrupted from the inside, or the out that will last as long as humanity exists. <br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We believe our core function, or recording human history of the people. by the people for the people, will allow us to achieve what we have listed above. We may not live to see the results of what we are setting out to do, but we fully understand the importance of planting trees that we will not eat the fruit from. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":136,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2018-10-04-26.png\" alt=\"Goals unifying the human race\" class=\"wp-image-136\"/><figcaption>People of the world coming together </figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Vision and goals', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:06:49', '2020-12-14 12:06:49', '', 54, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/54-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(246, 1, '2020-12-14 12:49:45', '2020-12-14 12:49:45', '{\n    \"graphene_settings[top_bar_bg]\": {\n        \"value\": \"#0f0909\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2020-12-14 12:49:30\"\n    },\n    \"graphene_settings[top_bar_fg]\": {\n        \"value\": \"#ffffff\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2020-12-14 12:49:35\"\n    },\n    \"graphene_settings[top_bar_link]\": {\n        \"value\": \"#6935ad\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2020-12-14 12:49:45\"\n    }\n}', '', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2565d606-57f2-412b-b357-c2df9d0eec4d', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:49:45', '2020-12-14 12:49:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/?p=246', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
(247, 1, '2020-12-14 12:51:54', '2020-12-14 12:51:54', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At the beginning of July 2017, I took the first step (leap of faith!) in the THC direction. For the first time in my life I traveled abroad on my own, to Croatia, where I met and stayed with people that I had only ever spoken to online. The flight out was ok, and I had a great conversation with the driver who drove me from Zagreb to Osijek, we are now friends and are meeting up soon!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When I arrived at Domagojs place and we met for the first time in person, I instantly felt as if I had been around him before  as if I had known his presence in a way. We went inside, and I got to meet his lovely partner and eat some delicious food. Later that night we went for a meal and I had the opportunity to meet the other 2 team members that Domagoj had recruited to help out: Designer Davor and Back End Developer Davor. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We spoke about THC whilst also getting to know one another and it was a really good night. After dinner, Domagoj took me to meet Alen, the man who I would be staying with whilst I was there. Even though we never met, we had a long chat and completely hit it off. I had a great time and felt very welcome/safe whilst staying there.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whilst in Osijek, Designer Davor and his wife kept me entertained throughout the day showing me around the local sites and Domagojs partner took me to the local market where I got to meet her parents  such lovely people. I had a really great time. One of the evenings we dedicated to The Human Codex by holding our first team Scrum  we ordered food and went in to detail about The Human Codex, what it is, what it will do, and what it will become. I think for the first time the team got to see the passion behind THC and why the task of getting it live has never stopped.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I came back from Croatia full of positive thoughts and for the first time realised what I had been envisioning for so long, will actual come true by the end of the year. Unfortunately, things took a slight turn when the Designer advised us that he had another commitment, which meant that he would no longer be able to dedicate the necessary time to THC. Luckily for us, Domagoj was quick to find someone else to help and now we are more confident than ever that THC will be created and become everything that we hope it to be but I had no idea where it would lead me.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":228,\"width\":500,\"height\":500,\"sizeSlug\":\"thumbnail\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-thumbnail is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/bumpy-road-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Two steps back, one  leap forward\" class=\"wp-image-228\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\"/><figcaption>Two steps back, one  leap forward</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Two Steps back one leap forward', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '83-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-12-14 12:51:54', '2020-12-14 12:51:54', '', 83, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/83-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
